  "local_port": 42604,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are the best Hindi songs to sing?",
  "response": "Choosing the best Hindi songs to sing largely depends on your personal taste, vocal range, and the occasion. Whether you're looking for classics to showcase your vocal prowess, romantic tunes to set a mood, or peppy numbers to energize the crowd, there's something for everyone. Here's a curated list across various genres and eras to help you find the perfect song to sing:\n\n### **Classic Bollywood Hits**\n1. **\"Tujh Mein Rab Dikhta Hai\"** from *Rab Ne Bana Di Jodi*  \n   *A soulful and melodic track that's perfect for showcasing emotional depth.*\n\n2. **\"Chura Liya Hai Tumne Jo Dil Ko\"** from *Yaadon Ki Baaraat*  \n   *A timeless romantic song with a catchy tune.*\n\n3. **\"Lag Ja Gale\"** from *Woh Kaun Thi?*  \n   *A beautiful ghazal-style song ideal for slower, more expressive singing.*\n\n4. **\"Pal Pal Dil Ke Paas\"** from *Blackmail*  \n   *A soothing melody that's great for heartfelt performances.*\n\n### **Modern Bollywood Hits**\n1. **\"Tum Hi Ho\"** from *Aashiqui 2*  \n   *A contemporary romantic ballad that's widely loved.*\n\n2. **\"Kalank Title Track\"** from *Kalank*  \n   *A powerful and dynamic song suitable for dramatic performances.*\n\n3. **\"Bekhayali\"** from *Kabir Singh*  \n   *An intense and passionate track perfect for emotive singing.*\n\n4. **\"Shayad\"** from *Love Aaj Kal (2020)*  \n   *A soft and melodious song ideal for romantic renditions.*\n\n### **Peppy and Upbeat Songs**\n1. **\"Gallan Goodiyaan\"** from *Dil Dhadakne Do*  \n   *An energetic song that's excellent for group performances.*\n\n2. **\"Badtameez Dil\"** from *Yeh Jawaani Hai Deewani*  \n   *A high-energy track perfect for lively singing sessions.*\n\n3. **\"London Thumakda\"** from *Queen*  \n   *A fun and catchy song that's great for celebrations.*\n\n4. **\"Kala Chashma\"** from *Baar Baar Dekho*  \n   *A trendy and upbeat number perfect for parties.*\n\n### **Romantic Ballads**\n1. **\"Ae Dil Hai Mushkil\"** from *Ae Dil Hai Mushkil*  \n   *A deep and emotional song ideal for expressing feelings.*\n\n2. **\"Pehla Nasha\"** from *Jo Jeeta Wohi Sikandar*  \n   *A classic romantic tune perfect for serenades.*\n\n3. **\"Raabta\"** from *Agent Vinod*  \n   *A melodious song that's great for heartfelt performances.*\n\n4. **\"Janam Janam\"** from *Dilwale*  \n   *A beautiful love song with rich musicality.*\n\n### **Sufi and Folk-Inspired Songs**\n1. **\"Kun Faya Kun\"** from *Rockstar*  \n   *A spiritually uplifting song with powerful vocals.*\n\n2. **\"Teri Mitti\"** from *Kesari*  \n   *A patriotic song with deep emotional resonance.*\n\n3. **\"Maula Mere Maula\"** from *Anwar*  \n   *A soulful track perfect for expressive singing.*\n\n4. **\"Sajde\"** from *Kill Dil*  \n   *A melodious song with a soothing vibe.*\n\n### **Contemporary Indie and Fusion**\n1. **\"Tum Se Hi\"** by Mohit Chauhan  \n   *A modern romantic song with a fresh melody.*\n\n2. **\"Pachtaoge\"** by Arijit Singh  \n   *A passionate song that's great for contemporary performances.*\n\n3. **\"Dil Dhadakne Do\"** by Priyanka Chopra & Farhan Akhtar  \n   *A vibrant track blending traditional and modern sounds.*\n\n4. **\"Khairiyat\"** by Arijit Singh  \n   *A heartfelt song with emotional depth.*\n\n### **Tips for Choosing the Right Song:**\n- **Vocal Range:** Select a song that fits comfortably within your vocal range to ensure a confident performance.\n- **Emotion and Expression:** Choose a song that you connect with emotionally, as this will enhance your delivery.\n- **Practice:** Familiarize yourself with the lyrics and melody to perform the song smoothly.\n- **Occasion Appropriateness:** Consider the setting\u2014whether it's a casual sing-along, a formal performance, or a celebration\u2014and choose a song that suits the mood.\n\nRemember, the best song to sing is one that resonates with you and allows you to express yourself authentically. Happy singing!",
